## Requirements
 - Python3
 - tensorflow2
 - gym
 - tqdm

## Usage
  - clone this repo
 ```
 $ git clone https://github.com/morikatron/PPO.git
 ```
  - change directory and run 
 ```
 $ cd PPO
 $ python algo/run.py
 ```
